data.description: This beautiful home on the north side of Evansville offers a fantastic living experience; with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, it's the perfect place to call home. Nestled in a private setting with a charming tree-lined backyard and a fully fenced-in yard, you'll enjoy the tranquility and privacy of this location. The recent addition of a brand new roof ensures the home is in great condition. As you step inside, you'll be welcomed by a spacious foyer. The large formal dining room boasts crown molding and wainscoting. The living room is a standout feature of this home, with its two-story ceilings, gas fireplace, and built-ins. The eat-in kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ample cabinets, a pantry, and a convenient center island for preparing and enjoying meals. The main floor also includes a half bath and an attached 2-car garage. The spacious primary bedroom is a true retreat. It features a large walk-in closet and a full bath with a jetted tub and a step-in shower. The upper level includes two guest bedrooms and a full bath, laundry room and new carpet has also been installed in a guest bedroom and staircase. Outside, you'll find an extended porch and a stone pathway leading to a cozy firepit. For your peace of mind, a one-year home warranty is being provided to the new buyer. This home is a true gem, offering comfort, style, and a welcoming atmosphere.
